peculations%20that%20her%20earrings%20were%20actually%20Icebach%20Sound%20Solutions'%20Nova%20H1%20Audio%20Earrings%2C%20a%20Bluetooth%20device%20designed%20to%20look%20like%20jewellery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20fuelling%20the%20speculation%2C%20Icebach's%20managing%20director%2C%20Malte%20Iversen%2C%20reportedly%20said%20to%20tech%20outlet%20Tom's%20Guide%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20know%20whether%20Mrs%20Harris%20wore%20one%20of%20our%20products.%20The%20resemblance%20is%20striking.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20humorously%20offered%20to%20create%20a%20male%20version%20of%20the%20device%20for%20Trump%2C%20suggesting%20that%20the%20colour%20orange%20posed%20a%20design%20challenge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%F0%9F%9A%A8%F0%9F%9A%A8KAMALA%20HARRIS%20EXPOSED%20FOR%20WEARING%20EARPIECE%20IN%20DEBATE%20*PROOF%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnShe%20is%20seen%20wearing%20an%20earring%20developed%20by%20Nova%20Audio%20Earrings%20first%20seen%20at%20CES%202023.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20earring%20has%20audio%20transmission%20capabilities%20and%20acts%20as%20a%20discreet%20earpiece.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnKamala%20Harris%20confirms%20claims%20that%20a%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F1y60rUdJT0%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F1y60rUdJT0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ELECTION2024%20%F0%9F%87%BA%F0%9F%87%B8%20(%4024ELECTIONS)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F24ELECTIONS%2Fstatus%2F1833720721056669807%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20viral%20claims%2C%20experts%20and%20fact-checkers%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20Harris's%20actual%20earrings%20are%20the%20Double%20Pearl%20Hinged%20Earrings%20from%20Tiffany%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20which%20retail%20for%20approximately%20%24800.%20These%20earrings%20bear%20little%20resemblance%20to%20Icebach's%20Bluet