ed%20so.%20I%20had%20only%20campaigned%20for%20my%20son%20(Naveen%20Jindal%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabah%20polls).%20I%20have%20not%20taken%20any%20membership%20(of%20the%20BJP)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESavitri%20Jindal%20was%20elected%20as%20an%20MLA%20from%20the%20Hisar%20seat%20twice.%20She%20became%20represented%20Hisar%20in%20the%20Haryana%20Assembly%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202005%20as%20a%20Congress%20MLA.%20She%20was%20reelected%20from%20the%20seat%20in%202009%20and%20was%20made%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Singh%20Hooda%20government%20in%202013.%20She%20quit%20the%20Congress%20in%20March%20this%20year%20when%20her%20son%20Naveen%20Jindal%20also%20left%20the%20party%20and%20later%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726190460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fbt6vc99o_savitri-jindal_625x300_13_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-assembly-elections-indias-richest-woman-savitri-jindal-to-contest-as-independent-from-hisar-6553449%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP's%20Kurukshetra%20MP%20Naveen%20Jindal's%20mother%20Savitri%20Jindal%2C%20who%20was%20an%20aspirant%20of%20a%20poll%20ticket%20from%20the%20party%20for%20the%20Haryana%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20filed%20her%20nomination%20from%20the%20Hisar%20seat%20as%20an%20Independent%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CAA%20and%20Wasserman%20Foundation%20Partner%20to%20Launch%20School%20Day%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726190281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCAA-Co-Chairman-Richard-L