2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20plenty%20of%20Airbnb%20hosts%20happily%20help%20me%20decide%20on%20a%20restaurant%20for%20dinner%20or%20offer%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisiting-national-park-first-time-surprising-things-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecommendations%20on%20nearby%20hikes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20until%20my%20recent%20travels%2C%20I%20had%20never%20stayed%20in%20a%20hotel%20with%20a%20concierge%20desk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20high-end%20hotels%2C%20there's%20an%20entire%20team%20willing%20to%20create%20your%20vacation%20itinerary.%20I%20initially%20feared%20a%20concierge%20desk%20would%20be%20outdated%2C%20but%20the%20staff%20I%20met%20at%20both%20the%20Fairmont%20Chateau%20Lake%20Louise%20and%20The%20Little%20Nell%20were%20seasonal%20workers%20my%20age%20with%20local%20suggestions%20targeted%20for%20young%20travelers%20like%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20arriving%20at%20The%20Little%20Nell%2C%20the%20concierge%20desk%20scheduled%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-house-tavern-restaurant-review-aspen-leonardo-dicaprio-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweek's%20worth%20of%20dinner%20reservations%3C%2Fa%3E.%20All%20I%20had%20to%20do%20was%20pick%20the%20restaurants%20and%20the%20times%2C%20and%20they%20did%20the%20rest.%20When%20my%20plans%20changed%2C%20I%20simply%20stopped%20by%20the%20desk%2C%20told%20them%20what%20I%20needed%20to%20be%20updated%2C%20and%20they%20made%20the%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20familiar%20with%20the%20concierge%20desk's%20extravagance.%20There%20was%20no%20waiting%20on%20hold%20with%20the%20restaurant%20or%20dealing%20with%20confusing%20reservation%20schedules.%20It%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20a%20personal%20assistant%20throughout%20my%20stays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20incorrectly%20assumed%20microwaves%20were%20a%20standard%20in%20every%20hotel%20%E2%80%94%20no%20matter%20the%20rating.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20open%20closet%20at%20The%20Little%20Nell%20hotel%20in%20Aspen%2C%20Colorado.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61f8113e415c3f0018d3b53b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20closet%20at%20The%20Little%20Nell%20hotel%20in%20Aspen%2C%20Colorado.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20grew%20up%20staying%20in%20budget%20hotels%20and%20motels%2C%20plastic%20cups%20wrapped%20in%20plastic%20were%20the%20norm%2C%20cheap%20ice%20buckets%20were%20expected%2C%20and%20there%20was%20always%20a%20microwave%20in%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFast-forward%20to%20staying%20at%20The%20Little%20Nell%2C%20and%20it%20felt%20like%20something%20was%20missing.%20It%20wasn't%20until%20my%20friend%20got%20cold%20tomato%20soup%20from%20a%20restaurant%20that%20we%20realized%20there%20wasn't%20a%20microwave%20in%20sight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20six%20luxury%20hotels%20I%20stayed%20at%20lacked%20an%20in-room%20microwave%2C%20which%20felt%20surprising%20considering%20other%20appliances%20like%20coffee%20machines%20and%20dehumidifiers%20were%20provided.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20later%20learned%20that%20most%20hotels%20have%20microwaves%20available%2C%20you%20just%20have%20to%20request%20one%20from%20the%20front%20desk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20learned%20that%20luxury%20hotels%20often%20have%20a%20scent%20that%20is%20unique%20to%20their%20brand.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20lobby%20of%20The%20Darling%20hotel%20had%20a%20citrusy%20scent.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F639354028580f70019f82d25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20lobby%20of%20The%20Darling%20hotel%20had%20a%20citrusy%20scent.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20friend%20and%20I%20stepped%20into%20the%20Fairmont%20Lake%20Louise%2C%20we%20were%20hit%20with%20a%20woodsy%2C%20flowery%20smell.%20Initially%2C%20we%20assumed%20it%20was%20a%20waft%20of%20perfume%20from%20another%20guest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20adventuring%20outside%20and%20returning%20to%20the%20lobby%20hours%20later%2C%20the%20delightful%20smell%20remained.%20We%20spotted%20a%20lit%20candle%20in%20a%20corner%20that%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20source.%20We%20loved%20the%20scent%20so%20much%20that%20we%20headed%20to%20the%20front%20desk%20to%20ask%20about%20the%20candle%20and%20if%20we%20could%20buy%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20staff%20member%20kindly%20tracked%20it%20down%20and%20told%20us%20it%20was%20scents%20of%20black%20orchid%20and%20sage.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20hotel%20didn't%20sell%20its%20personalized%20candle%2C%20and%20we%20couldn't%20track%20it%20online.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%20a%20year%20later%20when%20I%20stepped%20into%20The%20Darling%2C%20I%20was%20once%20again%20enamored%20by%20a%20scent.%20This%20time%20it%20was%20sweet%20orange%2C%20grapefruit%20zest%2C%20rose%2C%20green%20tea%2C%20honey%2C%20and%20cedarwood.%20The%20hotel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Ftravel%2Fdestinations%2Foceania%2Faustralia%2Fnew-south-wales%2Fsydney%2Fhotels%2Fthe-darling-hotel%2F%5C%22%3Epumps%20the%20signature%20smell%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20Air%20Aroma%20diffusion%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20staying%20in%20five-star%20hotels%2C%20I%20never%20questioned%20a%20lobby's%20smell%2C%20unless%20it%20was%20musty%20or%20damp.%20Now%2C%20when%20I%20step%20into%20any%20hotel%20lobby%2C%20I%20immediately%20sniff%20in%20hopes%20of%20discovering%20a%20welcoming%2C%20unique%20scent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20was%20confused%20to%20find%20phones%20in%20the%20bathroom%20at%20two%20of%20the%20hotels.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Phones%20were%20next%20to%20the%20toilets%20in%20both%20The%20Little%20Nell%20and%20The%20St.%20Regis%20Aspen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61f8132b415c3f0018d3b614%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPhones%20were%20next%20to%20the%20toilets%20in%20both%20The%20Little%20Nell%20and%20The%20St.%20Regis%20Aspen.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDial%20phones%20often%20feel%20out%20of%20place%2C%20but%20I%20was%20even%20more%20surprised%20to%20find%20phones%20next%20to%20the%20toilet%20in%20both%20of%20my%20Aspen%20hotels.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20common%20item%20many%20hotels%20added%20to%20indicate%20luxury%20in%20the%201980s%20and%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOriginally%20phones%20in%20hotel%20bathrooms%20were%20installed%20for%20the%20convenience%20of%20guests%20who%20might%20be%20expecting%20a%20call%2C%20but%20the%20safety%20aspect%20of%20having%20a%20hotel%20bathroom%20phone%20was%20also%20very%20apparent%20and%20this%20remains%20the%20case%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Jonathan%20Toni%2C%20CEO%20of%20London-based%20Hotel%20Technology%20International%20Ltd%2C%20which%20makes%20and%20supplies%20hotels%20with%20toilet%20telephones%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Ftravel%2Ftravel-truths%2Fcurious-reason-hotels-have-always-put-phones-toilet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20telephone%20in%20The%20Little%20Nell's%20bathroom%20was%20the%20only%20one%20I%20could%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20work.%20So%20when%20I%20had%20a%20question%20about%20the%20hotel's%20valet%20service%2C%20I%20went%20to%20the%20bathroom%20to%20make%20my%20call.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20didn't%20previously%20know%20that%20some%20five-star%20hotels%20have%20ritzy