service%20simply%20involves%20prepping%20your%20room%20for%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20the%20staff%20will%20pull%20down%20blankets%20and%20fluff%20pillows%2C%20clear%20out%20trash%2C%20replace%20towels%2C%20and%20hopefully%20leave%20a%20chocolate%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20staff%20at%20The%20Little%20Nell%20asked%20about%20turn-down%20service%2C%20I%20opted%20out%20because%20I%20didn't%20want%20unnecessary%20contact%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20I%20did%2C%20however%2C%20opt%20in%20for%20the%20chocolate%20the%20staff%20offered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPersonally%2C%20turn-down%20service%20feels%20superfluous%20for%20a%20single-night%20stay%2C%20but%20if%20my%20hotel%20reservations%20had%20been%20longer%2C%20I%20would%20have%20opted%20in.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20five-star%20hotels%20I%20stayed%20at%20included%20lots%20of%20extra%20amenities%20like%20free%20car%20rentals%20and%20hiking%20gear.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222021%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20friend%20holds%20a%20pair%20of%20microspikes%2C%20which%20we%20didn't%20end%20up%20using%20on%20our%20snow%20hike.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e32615cfb7f307e5710602%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221516%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20friend%20holds%20a%20pair%20of%20microspikes%2C%20which%20they%20borrowed%20for%20free%20from%20the%20hotel.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20that%20the%20luxuries%20of%20five-star%20hotels%20often%20extended%20well%20beyond%20my%20hotel%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Fairmont%20Chateau%20Lake%20Louise%2C%20my%20friend%20and%20I%20went%20to%20the%20concierge%20desk%20to%20ask%20for%20hike%20recommendations.%20While%20there%2C%20a%20staff%20member%20let%20us%20know%20that%20we%20could%20rent%20microspikes%2C%20which%20are%20helpful