20Nell%2C%20I%20paid%20a%20%2442%20resort%20fee%20in%20addition%20to%20my%20%24719%20room%20cost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFive-star%20hotels%20often%20have%20many%20lauded%20restaurants%20and%20shops%20attached%20to%20their%20buildings.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20interior%20of%20the%20Kingi%20restaurant%20at%20the%20Hotel%20Britomart.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63935614d089dd0019bbdfc2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20interior%20of%20the%20Kingi%20restaurant%20at%20the%20Hotel%20Britomart.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20theory%2C%20I%20never%20needed%20to%20leave%20any%20of%20the%20five-star%20hotels%20during%20my%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fairmont%20Chateau%20Lake%20Louise%2C%20The%20Little%20Nell%2C%20The%20St.%20Regis%20Aspen%2C%20The%20Darling%2C%20and%20Hotel%20Britomart%20all%20had%20multiple%20dining%20options%20inside%20their%20buildings.%20And%2C%20these%20restaurants%20were%20recognized%20as%20some%20of%20the%20best%20in%20each%20respective%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20multiple%20people%20urged%20me%20to%20order%20the%20truffle%20fries%20at%20Ajax%20Tavern%2C%20a%20restaurant%20connected%20to%20The%20Little%20Nell.%20In%20Lake%20Louise%2C%20my%20friend%20and%20I%20dined%20at%20the%20Alpine%20Social%2C%20one%20of%20the%20hotel's%20six%20restaurants%2C%20and%20had%20no%20regrets%20about%20our%20choice.%20And%20one%20of%20the%20best%20meals%20I%20had%20in%20Auckland%20was%20a%20rosti%20with%20smoked%20fish%20and%20poached%20eggs%20at%20Kingi%2C%20a%20restaurant%20inside%20Hotel%20Britomart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20restaurants%2C%20many%20of%20the%20five-star%20hotels%20also%20had%20shopping.%20The%20St.%20Regis%20Aspen%20had%20jewelry%20stores%2C%20The%20Little%20Nell%20had%20an%20art%20gallery%2C%20and%20the%20Fairmont%20had%20its%20