20financial%20institutions%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbofa-banker-leo-lukenas-wanted-new-job-better-hours-reuters-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELukenas'%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%20shook%20Wall%20Street%20in%20part%20because%20he%20was%20a%2035-year-old%20former%20Green%20Beret%2C%20presumed%20to%20be%20strong%20and%20fit.%20Even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdimon-said-bofa-bankers-death-sparked-questions-inside-jpmorgan-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJamie%20Dimon%2C%20CEO%20of%20JPMorgan%20Chase%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20addressed%20the%20death%20at%20an%20investor%20presentation%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20bank's%20leadership%20had%20been%20conferring%20to%20understand%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20can%20we%20learn%20from%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20capping%20or%20closely%20tracking%20hours%20sounds%20good%20in%20theory%2C%20insiders%20said%20it%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20enforce.%20Indeed%2C%20banks%20have%20been%20down%20this%20road%20before%20%E2%80%94%20promising%20change%20and%20rolling%20out%20new%20guardrails%20%E2%80%94%20only%20to%20land%20back%20in%20the%20same%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20fantastic%20that%20they're%20taking%20the%20concerns%20of%20junior%20bankers%20seriously%20and%20taking%20the%20situation%20that%20happened%20this%20summer%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20junior%20banker%20who%20left%20Bank%20of%20America%20last%20year%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20speaking%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20to%20protect%20her%20career.%20But%20the%20nature%20of%20investment%20banking%20work%20makes%20it%20hard%20to%20believe%20that%20such%20guardrails%20will%20stand%20the%20test%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20track%20hours%20and%20promise%20days%20off%2C%20but%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20if%20there's%20work%20to%20get%20done%20and%20the%20expectation%20is%20that%20it's%20coming%20from%20your%20senior%20banker%20because%20a%20client%20needs%20it%2C%20that's%20going%20to%20get%20done.%20That's%20how%20they%20make%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Bank%20of%20America%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20new%20platform%20has%20been%20in%20the%20works%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%20and%20allows%20for%20more%20efficient%2C%20daily%20reporting%20by%20BofA%20employees.%20In%20response%20to%20enforcement%20concerns%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BOur%20practices%20are%20clear%20and%20we%20expect%20all%20employees%20and%20managers%20to%20follow%20them.%20When%20we've%20learned%20of%20violations%20disciplinary%20actions%20have%20been%20taken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20incoming%20investment%20banking%20analyst%2C%20who%20also%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20to%20protect%20his%20job%20prospects%2C%20described%20the%20changes%20as%20%26quot%3Bsaving%20face.%26quot%3B%20He%20completed%20an%20internship%20at%20an%20investment%20bank%20in%20New%20York%20last%20summer%20and%20accepted%20a%20return%20offer%20to%20start%20full%20time%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20sad%20it%20took%20someone's%20death%20to%20make%20this%20shockwave%20throughout%20Wall%20Street%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20reality%2C%20nothing%20is%20going%20to%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b4622e9b-71ad-4923-97d1-bf36122f745d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorking%20a%20live%20deal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJuniors%20are%20incentivized%20to%20outwork%20each%20other%20because%20their%20manager's%20opinion%20of%20them%20determines%20their%20year-end%20bonus%2C%20the%20deals%20they%20get%20staffed%20on%2C%20and%20the%20work%20they%20get%20assigned.%20In%20trying%20to%20impress%20that%20person%20with%20their%20work%20ethic%2C%20they%20could%20end%20up%20feeling%20pressured%20to%20go%20against%20the%20very%20guardrail%20that's%20supposed%20to%20protect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20finance%20professor%20who%20teaches%20aspiring%20investment%20bankers%20at%20a%20top%20business%20school%20explained%20it%20this%20way%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20develop%20a%20reputation%20as%20being%20the%20person%20who%20always%20calls%2080%20hours%20a%20week%2C%20and%20suddenly%20you're%20the%20lowest%20analyst%20getting%20all%20the%20worst%20work.%20Unless%20there's%20buy-in%20at%20the%20top%20that%20this%20is%20the%20best%20thing%20to%20do%2C%20nothing%20changes.%26quot%3B%20The%20professor%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20to%20protect%20his%20students'%20job%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20skepticism%20over%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20these%20policies%20are%20some%20of%20the%20key%20exceptions%20being%20built%20into%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20WSJ%20outlined%20that%20JPMorgan's%20new%20capped-hours%20policy%20has%20%26quot%3Bexceptions%20for%20certain%20circumstances%2C%20such%20as%20a%20live%20deal.%26quot%3B%20The%20Journal%20said%20JPMorgan%20is%20also%20giving%20US%20juniors%20get%20%26quot%3Bone%20protected%20full%20weekend%20off%20every%20three%20months%2C%20plus%20protected%20holidays%20with%20guaranteed%20time%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20mandating%20%26quot%3Bpencils%20down%26quot%3B%20between%206%20p.m.%20Friday%20and%20noon%20Saturday%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bwith%20exceptions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incoming%20analyst%20and%20professor%20said%20such%20caveats%20stand%20to%20render%20policies%20moot%20because%20live%20deals%20are%20precisely%20when%20overwork%20becomes%20a%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20the%20extent%20that%20there's%20an%20ebb%20and%20a%20flow%20in%20live%20deals%2C%20then%20the%2080-hour%20cap%20at%20least%20prevents%20an%20MD%20from%20working%20you%20100%20hours%20a%20week%20while%20they're%20frantically%20pitching%20to%20try%20and%20win%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20professor%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20for%20a%20busy%20group%20that's%20always%20on%20live%20deals%20that%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20out%20and%20pitch%2C%20then%20it's%20nothing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20a%20cap%20on%20working%20hours%2C%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20disappoint%20their%20boss.%20If%20senior%20banking%20staff%20don't%20unilaterally%20enforce%20the%20cap%20and%20take%20it%20seriously%2C%20junior%20bankers%20can%20feel%20pressure%20to%20let%20the%20rules%20slide%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20the%20team%20and%20their%20own%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20concern%20is%20that%20it%20won't%20be%20enforced%2C%20that%20there%20will%20be%20too%20many%20dynamics%20within%20the%20office%20of%20not%20wanting%20to%20report%20to%20HR%20if%20a%20junior%20banker%20is%20being%20pressured%20to%20work%20extra%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20incoming%20analyst.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e7e93d60-27e0-4c11-ae35-3ed5ef06fa50%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBofA's%202014%20death%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20is%20having%20HR%20notified%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20hours%20worked%20exceed%2080%20a%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20intervening%20%26quot%3Bafter%20prolonged%20periods%20above%20that%20limit%20to%20mandate%20time%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20offering%20a%20%26quot%3Bprotected%20weekend%20day%20of%20no%20work%2C%20with%20no%20specific%20time%20frame%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20modification%20of%20a%20process%20the%20bank%20adopted%20in%202014%20following%20the%20sudden%20death%20of%20an%20intern%20in%20London.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-21-year-old-bofa-intern-has-died-2013-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMoritz%20Erhardt%3C%2Fa%3E%20died%20after%20what%20was%20later%20determined%20to%20be%20an%20epileptic%20seizure%20that%20may%20have%20been%20triggered%20by%20fatigue.%20He%20had%20been%20spending%20long%20days%20in%20the%20office%20and%20reports%20at%20the%20time%20suggested%