At%20her%20creative%20peak%2C%20Perry's%20lyrics%20were%20cheeky%2C%20her%20melodies%20stickier%20than%20anyone's.%20Even%20as%20I'm%20writing%20this%2C%20the%20morning%20after%20the%20VMAs%2C%20I've%20repeatedly%20caught%20myself%20humming%2C%20%26quot%3BKiss%20me%2C%20k-k-kiss%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20highlight%20was%20easily%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F98WtmW-lfeE%3Fsi%3DCYWecdg0SgVdh0kk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETeenage%20Dream%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20title%20track%20from%20Perry's%202010%20album%20and%20one%20of%20the%20most%20perfectly%20constructed%20pop%20songs%20of%20all%20time.%20After%20the%20show%20ended%20hours%20later%2C%20I%20heard%20a%20girl%20say%20in%20a%20hushed%2C%20reverent%20tone%2C%20%26quot%3BBeing%20so%20close%20to%20Katy%20Perry%20singing%20'Teenage%20Dream'%20was%E2%80%A6%20surreal.%26quot%3B%20And%20it%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c4ae5388-60a3-4d25-b194-23b1c7f2886f%5C%22%3EFans%20are%20waiting%20to%20see%20if%20Perry's%20next%20album%20can%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20legacy%20she's%20created%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sheer%20power%20of%20Perry's%20early%20discography%20on%20display%20last%20night%20was%20both%20her%20triumph%20and%20her%20downfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerry%20has%20timeless%20hits%20in%20her%20catalog.%20No%20one%20can%20take%20that%20away%20from%20her.%20But%20by%20mixing%20them%20into%20a%20medley%20with%20singles%20from%20%26quot%3B143%2C%26quot%3B%20Perry's%20latest%20work%20sounds%20even%20more%20hollow%20and%20derivative%20by%20comparison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerry's%20collaboration%20with%20Doechii%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20His%2C%20He's%20Mine%2C%26quot%3B%20out%20tomorrow%2C%20had%20the%20misfortune%20of%20being%20sandwiched%20in%20between%20%26quot%3BET%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF57P9C4SAW4%3Fsi%3D1uUSYKvaJuKkFcsj%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECalifornia%20Gurls%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20There's%20not