0year%2C%20five%20new%20countries%20-%20Iran%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Egypt%2C%20UAE%20and%20Ethiopia%20-%20joined%20the%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20the%20club%3F%20Because%20there%20was%20another%20club.%20It%20was%20called%20the%20G7%20and%20you%20will%20not%20let%20anybody%20else%20into%20that%20club.%20So%2C%20we%20go%20and%20form%20our%20own%20club%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20foreign%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20still%20struck%20by%20how%20insecure%20the%20(Global)%20North%20is%20when%20you%20speak%20about%20the%20BRICS.%20Somehow%2C%20something%20seems%20to%20get%20under%20people's%20skin%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHere's%20an%20observation.%20There%20is%20a%20G20%2C%20did%20the%20G7%20disband%3F%20Has%20it%20stopped%20meeting%3F%20No%2C%20it%20still%20continues.%20So%2C%20the%20G20%20exists%2C%20but%20the%20G7%20still%20exists.%20Then%2C%20why%20can't%20the%20G20%20be%20there%20and%20the%20BRICS%20also%20exist%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20also%20talked%20about%20the%20Global%20South.%20%26quot%3BThe%20countries%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20most%20of%20them%20are%20decolonised%20countries.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20developing%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%20He%20termed%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20intuitive%20gathering%20of%20countries%20who%20actually%20know%20why%20they%20are%20in%20that%20room%20and%20they%20have%20a%20feel%20for%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foreign%20minister%20is%20currently%20on%20the%20third%20and%20final%20leg%20of%20his%20three-nation%20tour.%20He%20started%20off%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20for%20the%20first%20India-Gulf%20Cooperation%20Council%20Ministerial%20Meeting%20and%20went%20on%20to%20visit%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20held%20wide-ranging%20talks%20with%20his%20German%20counterpart%2C%20Annalena%20Baerbock%2C%20and%20called%20on%20German%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scho