s%20to%20get%20together%20for%20a%20strategy%20session%20to%20negotiate%20a%20better%20financial%20deal%20for%20states%20that%20contribute%20more%20to%20the%20Central%20coffers.%20Besides%20the%20four%20southern%20states%20of%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Telangana%2C%20the%20list%20also%20includes%20Maharashtra%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Haryana%20and%20Punjab.%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah%20argues%20that%20higher%20income%20states%20are%20being%20pensalised%20for%20their%20economic%20performance.%20The%20current%20system%20undermines%20cooperative%20federalism%20and%20threatens%20financial%20autonomy%20of%20progressive%20states%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20Kerala%20counterpart%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20has%20said%20they%20must%20stand%20together%20and%20fight%2C%20arguing%20that%20fiscal%20federalism%20is%20in%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20comes%20ahead%20of%20the%2016th%20Finance%20Commission's%20move%20to%20finalise%20criterion%20for%20devolution%20of%20Central%20funds.%20Already%2C%20finance%20ministers%20of%20Telangana%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Punjab%20have%20met%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram%20to%20build%20consensus%20on%20their%20recommendations%20to%20the%20Finance%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20years%2C%20the%20tax%20share%20issue%20has%20been%20growing%20increasingly%20contentious%2C%20complicated%2C%20controversial%20and%20politically%20sensitive%2C%20with%20southern%20states%20getting%20increasingly%20vocal%20about%20getting%20an%20unfair%20deal%20despite%20their%20better%20performance.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20has%20said%20it%20receives%20just%2015%20paise%20for%20every%20rupee%20it%20contributes%20to%20the%20Union.%20Kerala%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20get%2025%20paise%20and%2029%20paise%20for%20every%20rupee%20they%20give.%20In%20comparison%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20gets%20Rs%202.73%20and%20Bihar%20receives%20Rs%207.06%20for%20every%20rupee%20they%20contributed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouthern%20states%20contribute%2030%20per%20cent%20to%20the%20GDP%2C%20have%2019.6%20per%20cent%20population.%20But%20tax%20devolution%20declined%20from%2021%20per%20cent%20under%2011th%20Finance%20Commission%20to%2015.8%20per%20cent%20under%20the%2014th%20Finance%20Commission.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20states%20are%20asking%20for%20a%20bigger%20share%20in%20central%20taxes.%20They%20say%20it%20should%20be%20hiked%20from%20the%20current%2041%20per%20cent%20to%2050%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20other%20demands%20and%20complaints%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESouthern%20states%20account%20for%2062%25%20of%20expenditure%20but%20get%2037%20per%20cent%20revenue%20share.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECess%2C%20surcharge%20account%20for%2028%20per%20cent%20of%20Central%20taxes%20and%20are%20not%20shared%20with%20states.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20states%20want%20a%20reduction%20in%20Centrally%20sponsored%20schemes%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20spend%20according%20to%20local%20priorities.%20Expenditure%20on%20Centrally%20sponsored%20schemes%20is%20more%20than%20three%20times%20the%20grants%20to%20states.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThey%20also%20say%20states%20that%20demographic%20discipline%20should%20not%20be%20punished.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20the%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Telangana%2C%20Bhatti%20Vikramarka%2C%20has%20sought%20that%20political%20representation%20of%20southern%20states%20be%20kept%20intact%20during%20delimitation.%20The%20good%20performance%20by%20states%20on%20population%20control%2C%20good%20governance%2C%20transparency%20should%20not%20be%20punished%2C%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSouthern%20states%2C%20despite%20their%20significant%20contribution%20to%20the%20GDP%20of%20over%2030%20per%20cent%20and%20representing%20a%20considerable%20portion%20of%20the%20population%20(19.6%25)%2C%20have%20seen%20their%20share%20in%20tax%20devolution%20decline%20from%2021.073%20per%20cent%20under%20the%20eleventh%20finance%20commission%20to%20just%2015.8%20per%20cent%20under%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726165740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F3rgcgk_siddaramaiah_625x300_17_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsiddaramaiah-seeks-9-state-strategy-session-on-central-funds-share-6552324%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Chief%20Ministers%20of%20eight%20states%20to%20get%20together%20for%20a%20strategy%20session%20to%20negotiate%20a%20better%20financial%20deal%20for%20states%20that%20contribute%20more%20to%20the%20Central%20coffers%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bush's%20attorney%20general%20says%20'I%20can't%20sit%20quietly'%2C%20endorses%20Kamala%20Harris%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726165646000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113301894%2Cimgsize-689063.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbushs-attorney-general-says-i-cant-sit-quietly-endorses-kamala-harris%2Farticleshow%2F113301807.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113301807.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EGonzales%20said%20he%20spoke%20with%20Trump%20only%20once%20and%20does%20not%20really%20know%20him.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20telling%2C%20however%2C%20that%20several%20senior%20officials%20who%20worked%20for%20him%20in%20the%20White%20House%20now%20refuse%20to%20support%20him%2C%20including%20his%20vice%20president%2C%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20defense%20secretary%20and%20national%20security%20adviser.%20Their%20unwillingness%20to%20endorse