ourney%20and%20Sultan%20Singh%20had%20given%20Rs%204%20lakh%20to%20the%20accused%20as%20his%20commission.%20It%20was%20also%20decided%20that%20the%20remaining%20amount%20would%20be%20paid%20after%20the%20passenger%20reached%20his%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20told%20police%20that%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Sultan%20Singh%20and%20other%20associates%2C%20he%20had%20made%20arrangements%20for%20the%20passenger's%20journey%20to%20the%20US%20five%20times%2C%20travelling%20through%20different%20countries%2C%20but%20the%20plan%20did%20not%20materialise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fifth%20attempt%20in%20March%2C%20the%20accused%20and%20other%20agents%20tried%20to%20send%20Gurpreet%20Singh%20to%20the%20US%20via%20Kazakhstan%20but%20the%20latter%20was%20caught%20by%20authorities%20in%20Kazakhstan%20and%20deported%20back%20to%20India%2C%20the%20DCP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kazakhastan%20authorities%20had%20suspected%20that%20the%20passenger%20was%20travelling%20on%20a%20fake%20visa%20as%20two%20pages%20of%20his%20passport%20were%20found%20to%20be%20torn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20found%20that%20in%20one%20of%20the%20previous%20attempts%2C%20Gurpreet%20Singh%20was%20provided%20with%20a%20fake%20Brazilian%20visa%20but%20was%20deported%20back%20to%20India%20from%20Qatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20two%20pages%20of%20the%20passport%20were%20removed%20by%20Sultan%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGurpreet%20Singh%20was%20interrogated%20and%20arrested%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20from%20the%20IGI%20airport%20in%20March.%20At%20his%20instance%2C%20Sultan%20Singh%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Punjab's%20Tarn%20Taran%2C%20was%20also%20arrested%20in%20March%20but%20Fatehjit%20Singh%20was%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DCP%20said%20investigation%20is%20on%20to%20unearth%20the%20involvement%20of%20other%20agents.%20The%20bank%20accounts%20of%20Fathejit%20Singh%20would%20be%20scrutinised%20to%20ascertain%20his%20possible%20involveme