ve%20steps%20against%20her%20for%20violating%20Constitutional%20provisions.%20My%20role%20as%20the%20Governor%20will%20be%20confined%20to%20the%20Constitutional%20obligations%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bose%20said%20in%20the%20video%20message.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20stand%20committed%20to%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Bengal%2C%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20victim%20of%20RG%20Kar%20and%20the%20people%20who%20are%20fighting%20for%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20my%20assessment%2C%20the%20government%20has%20failed%20in%20its%20duties...%20this%20is%20due%20to%20a%20big%20dilemma%20-%20that%20the%20health%20minister%20is%20the%20home%20minister%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20is%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20in%20a%20jibe%20at%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20holds%20the%20health%20and%20the%20home%20portfolios.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Governor%20also%20expressed%20anguish%20over%20the%20state%20government%20ignoring%20his%20advice%20to%20take%20action%20against%20Kolkata%20Police%20Commissioner%20Vineet%20Goyal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protesting%20students%20have%20blamed%20the%20city%20police%20chief%20for%20lapses%20in%20handling%20the%20probe%20into%20the%20rape-murder%20of%20a%20junior%20doctor%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20or%20CBI%20after%20directions%20from%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComplaints%20about%20multiple%20lapses%20have%20been%20made%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20has%20taken%20up%20the%20case%20on%20its%20own.%20The%20three-judge%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20has%20pointed%20out%20quite%20a%20few%2C%20including%20missing%20challans%20and%20incomplete%20postmortem%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20the%20police%20chief%20approached%20the%20case%20was%20highly%20suspicious%2C%20and%20can%20be%20described%20as%20a%20sort%20of%20%26quot%3Bcriminal%20activity%26quot%3B%20for%20which%20legal%20action%20should%20be%20taken%20against%20him%2C%20Mr%20Bose%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArguing%20that%20the%20Governor%20he%20cannot%20remain%20silent%20in%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20state%20Secretariat%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20suppress%20the%20distrust%20(of%20the%20people)%20for%20long.%20The%20truth%20will%20surface%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20fool%20some%20people%20for%20some%20time%2C%20but%20you%20cannot%20fool%20all%20the%20people%20all%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726159080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fufo5067o_bengal-governor-cv-ananda-bose_625x300_12_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flady-macbeth-bengal-governor-cv-ananda-bose-says-will-socially-boycott-mamata-banerjee-6551640%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengal%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%20has%20said%20he%20would%20socially%20boycott%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%20In%20practice%2C%20it%20translates%20to%20not%20sharing%20any%20public%20platform%20with%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20he%20added.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flady-macbeth-bengal-governor-cv-ananda-bose-says-will-socially-boycott-mamata-banerjee-6551640%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22DMK%20Backs%20Siddaramaiah's%20Proposal%20To%20Discuss%20%26quot%3BUnfair%26quot%3B%20Sharing%20Of%20Taxes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20come%20out%20in%20support%20of%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah's%20proposal%20to%20convene%20a%20conclave%20of%20chief%20ministers%20to%20discuss%20the%20%26quot%3Bunfair%26quot%3B%20sharing%20of%20taxes%20with%20states%20and%20fiscal%20federalism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%2C%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20several%20chief%20ministers%2C%20including%20those%20of%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Haryana%2C%20and%20Punjab%2C%20has%20highlighted%20what%20he%20called%20the%20unfair%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%20He%20has%20argued%20that%20states%20with%20higher%20gross%20state%20domestic%20product%20(GSDP)%20per%20capita%20are%20being%20penalised%20for%20their%20economic%20performance%20and%20receiving%20disproportionately%20low%20tax%20allocations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20Mr%20Siddaramaiah's%20concerns%2C%20DMK%20spokesperson%20SAS%20Hafeezullah%20said%20the%20party%20has%20already%20raised%20these%20issues%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu%20receives%20only%2029%20paise%20for%20every%20rupee%20of%20tax%20paid%20to%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hafeezullah%20further%20criticised%20the%20Union%20government%20for%20betraying%20states%20by%20bypassing%20the%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20(GST)%20and%20collecting%20cess%20without%20sharing%20it%20with%20them%2C%20and%20failing%20to%20uphold%20the%20constitutionally%20mandated%20fiscal%20federalism.%20He%20also%20accused%20the%20Centre%20of%20allocating%20too%20little%20to%20non-BJP%20ruled%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20welcoming%20Siddaramaiah's%20call%20in%20principle%2C%20Mr%20Hafeezullah%20rubbished%20the%20BJP's%20argument%20that%20states%2C%20including%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20receive%20a%20larger%20tax%20allocation%20than%20they%20did%20under%20the%20UPA.%20He%20emphasised%20that%20comparing%20the%20current%20funding%20to%20states%20against%20what%20it%20was%20during%20the%20UPA%20regime%20is%20like%20comparing%20apples%20to%20oranges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20that%20the%20NDA%20government's%20budget%20has%20increased%20threefold%20compared%20to%20the%20UPA%20era%2C%20and%20that%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20states%20were%20able%20to%20levy%20taxes%20because%20there%20was%20no%20GST.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20allies%20and%20part%20of%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20grouping.%20The%20alliance%20swept%20the%20recent%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20winning%20all%2039%20seats%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20with%20the%20DMK%20and%20Congress%20emerging%20victorious%20in%2022%20and%20nine%20seats%20respectively%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20specific%20question%20on%20whether%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20should%20not%20have%20boycotted%20the%20Niti%20Aayog%20meeting%20in%20July%20so%20that%20he%20could%20have%20pressed%20these%20issues%2C%20Mr%20Hafeezullah%20called%20the%20boycott%20a%20protest%20to%20expose%20the%20BJP%20and%20said%20the%20DMK%20has%20no%20regrets.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726158900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Facnhg56_siddaramaiah-pti_625x300_17_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdmk-backs-siddaramaiahs-proposal-to-discuss-unfair-sharing-of-taxes-6551631%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ruling%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20come%20out%20in%20support%20of%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah's%20proposal%20to%20convene%20a%20conclave%20of%20chief%20ministers%20to%20discuss%20the%20%26quot%3Bunfair%26quot%3B%20sharing%20of%20taxes%20with%20states%20and%20fiscal%20federalism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdmk-backs-siddaramaiahs-proposal-to-discuss-unfair-sharing-of-taxes-6551631%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20the%20(y)ear%20of%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%20Trump%20hears%20insults%20galore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726158824000%2C%22visual%22%