d.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fairtel-signs-pact-with-italian-telco-to-expand-capacity-in-submarine-cable-124091201220_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fairtel-signs-pact-with-italian-telco-to-expand-capacity-in-submarine-cable-124091201220_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fairtel-signs-pact-with-italian-telco-to-expand-capacity-in-submarine-cable-124091201220_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Like%20Bulldozing%20Laws%20Of%20Country'%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20On%20'Bulldozer%20Justice'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EComing%20down%20heavily%20on%20'bulldozer%20justice'%20for%20the%20second%20time%20this%20month%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20crime%20is%20no%20grounds%20for%20demolition%20of%20a%20property%20and%20such%20actions%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20running%20a%20bulldozer%20over%20the%20laws%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20a%20petition%20by%20Javed%20Ali%20Mehboobamiya%20Saeed%20of%20Gujarat's%20Kheda%20district%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Hrishikesh%20Roy%2C%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20and%20SVN%20Bhatti%20was%20told%20on%20Thursday%20that%20municipal%20officers%20had%20threatened%20to%20demolish%20his%20family's%20home%20with%20a%20bulldozer%20after%20a%20case%20of%20trespass%20was%20registered%20against%20him%20on%20September%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Saeed's%20lawyer%20told%20the%20court%20that%20revenue%20records%20of%20Kathlal%20village%2C%20where%20the%20home%20stands%2C%20showed%20that%20his%20client%20was%20a%20co-owner%20of%20the%20land.%20A%20resolution%20passed%20by%20the%20gram%20panchayat%20in%20August%202004%20granted%20permission%20to%20build%20a%20house%20on%20the%20land%2C%20where%20three%20generations%20of%20his%20family%20had%20been%20living%20for%20two%20decades.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20also%20cited%20the%20September%202%20order%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%20which%20it%20had%20proposed%20a%20set%20of%20guidelines%20to%20be%20followed%20before%20demolishing%20homes.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20both%20sides%2C%20the%20bench%20said%20that%20in%20a%20country%20where%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20state%20are%20governed%20by%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20a%20violation%20by%20a%20member%20of%20a%20family%20cannot%20invite%20action%20against%20other%20members%20of%20the%20family%20or%20their%20legally%20constructed%20residence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlleged%20involvement%20in%20a%20crime%20is%20no%20ground%20for%20demolition%20of%20a%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20only%20a%20case%20had%20been%20registered%20against%20Mr%20Saeed%20and%20it%20has%20to%20be%20proved%20in%20court%20through%20a%20legal%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20court%20cannot%20be%20oblivious%20to%20such%20demolition%20threats%2C%20which%20are%20inconceivable%20in%20a%20nation%20where%20law%20is%20supreme.%20Otherwise%20such%20actions%20may%20be%20seen%20as%20running%20a%20bulldozer%20over%20the%20laws%20of%20the%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20and%20sought%20its%20reply%20within%20four%20weeks.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20Mr%20Saeed's%20house%20cannot%20be%20demolished%20until%20further%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%202%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20KV%20Viswanathan%20had%20asked%20how%20a%20house%20could%20be%20demolished%20just%20because%20it%20belongs%20to%20an%20accused%20or%20even%20a%20convict%20in%20a%20criminal%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20can%20demolition%20be%20just%20because%20he%20is%20an%20accused%20or%20even%20a%20convict...%20If%20construction%20is%20unauthorised%2C%20fine.%20There%20has%20to%20be%20some%20streamlining.%20We%20will%20lay%20down%20a%20procedure.%20You%20are%20saying%20demolition%20only%20if%20violation%20of%20municipal%20laws.%20There%20is%20a%20need%20for%20guidelines%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20documented%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%20Stating%20that%20it%20would%20hear%20the%20matter%20again%20on%20September%2017%2C%20the%20court%20also%20invited%20suggestions%20for%20dealing%20with%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBulldozer%20Politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court's%20observations%20on%20September%202%20had%20also%20sparked%20an%20exchange%20of%20barbs%20among%20political%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20BJP%20is%20wiped%20out%20(after%20the%20Assembly%20election%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh)%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20government%20is%20formed%2C%20the%20bulldozers%20of%20the%20entire%20state%20will%20head%20towards%20Gorakhpur%2C%26quot%3B%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20had%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20home%20district%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20had%20said%20that%20only%20people%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bbulldozer-like%20capability%26quot%3B%20could%20operate%20the%20heavy%20machinery.%20%26quot%3BNot%20everyone's%20hands%20can%20fit...%20it%20requires%20both%20heart%20and%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20the%20initiator%20of%20the%20bulldozer%20being%20used%20as%20a%20political%20tool%20and%20had%20even%20used%20the%20machine%20in%20his%20campaign%20in%20the%202022%20state%20elections.%20Other%20BJP-ruled%20states%20then%20went%20on%20to%20adopt%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20playbook%20of%20demolishing%20the%20houses%20of%20criminals%20to%20send%20out%20a%20strong%20message%20against%20crime.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726154820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%2