%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-4-1725529102-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364554%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Empower%E2%80%99%20campaign%20involved%20homemakers%20from%20Kozhikode%20preparing%20specialities%20that%20were%20then%20sold%20across%20the%20city%20during%20Ramadan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20us%20back%20to%20one%20of%20their%20campaigns%20%E2%80%98Empower%20by%20Fulva%E2%80%99%20done%20in%20Ramadan%20this%20year%2C%20Sanu%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20a%20great%20idea%20to%20have%20people%20break%20their%20fasts%20with%20a%20complete%20meal%20of%20Kerala%20specialities%2C%20including%20snacks%20and%20juices%20made%20by%20homemakers.%20We%20united%20120%20homemakers%20from%20Kozhikode%20who%20would%20prepare%20the%20items%3B%20tied%20up%20with%20auto%20drivers%20who%20would%20bring%20the%20food%20to%20our%20facility%20where%20it%20was%20packaged%20and%20then%20sent%20to%20counters%20which%20were%20manned%20by%20student%20volunteers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20customers%20collected%20the%20boxes%20from%20these%20counters%20in%20Kozhikode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20homemakers%20Shabna%20who%20benefitted%20from%20the%20campaign%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363990%2Fsenior-citizen-homemaker-starts-food-business-mama-nourish-startup-to-sell-laddu-bars%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20first%20time%20being%20part%20of%20a%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20earned%20Rs%2030%2C000%20during%20this%20campaign%20in%20my%20free%20time!%E2%80%9D%20She%20adds%20that%20the%20experience%20was%20even%20more%20amazing%20as%20the%20earning%20was%20a%20product%20of%20her%20passion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%2